Announcement
To find out about the events that took place in the shattered scientist's mansion and to figure out where the red-skinned young man went, you have to try to get the necromancer's report.
#subobj 1
Get to the Citadel
The Citadel is the most protected place in the entire city of necromancers. It is located in the heart of the accommodation.
#subobj 2
Get an ad
The announcement of the Curse's assault on the scholars' property lies in a trunk at the extreme north end of the citadel.